# Benchmark artifacts. Tracked content under bench/ is infrastructure only
# (runner script, extractor, cleanup). Results, corpora, history, and
# scorecards stay local so private-repo names and case IDs never reach a
# commit by accident.
/bench/results-*
/bench/corpora/
/bench/history/
/bench/private/
/bench/*.scorecard.md
